    "Details": "A 3146 refit designed by the Republic of the Sphere for Julian Davion's personal honor guard, turned into a full production variant for the AFFS by StarCorps, the 7D replaces the 4S's weapons with an all-ClanTech arsenal. ExoStar Pinnacle lasers — dual ER medium lasers, a single medium pulse laser, and a centerpiece large pulse laser — are accompanied by a Type XX 'Great Bow' LRM-20 pack. The 4S's electronics suite is preserved, and CASE II is added to the ammo-laden right arm.<br><br>S-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that substantially improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
